    "7407225": {
        "Desc": "Talk to everyone",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "You don't seem to want to link the two of them together."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Neither elimination nor enumeration is very fair to Ann."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "What a coincidence. I happen to agree."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "But I have some other thoughts to share too, though they may have nothing to do with the next step in our reasoning."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "Are you willing to listen?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'm listening."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "Earlier, we broached the topic of Oceanid reproduction."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "It's a huge taboo for Oceanids to mimic and transform into one of their own kind, just as it is for humans to create humans."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "But you see... Humans can create humans. Through love."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "\"Go. Pursue eternity, not through mystery, but love.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "What if, by some chance, this mysterious method of Oceanid reproduction is accomplished through imagination and mimicry?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "Perhaps their regret or remorse gives birth to a thought, and as they imagine the path that could have been taken, a new Oceanid is born."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That's a very interesting idea."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "We'll never know. After all, it's a secret passed down amongst Oceanids only."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "In any case, we'll begin once you're ready."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
