    "7407501": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Seymour",
                    "T": "\"Lo, this place is the Orthant of Souls, the Shrine of Souls, the Room of Souls...\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Seymour",
                    "T": "\"I accompany you in eternal rest\"... \"Born in an instant, often contradicting, always united\"... \"I am life's most cherished treasure\"..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Phew... Nothing scary this time. Is the answer a pocket watch?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Speaking of which, don't you have one too, Ann?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Well, watches *are* expensive..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Then the answer must be money, as in Mora!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "Passing away along with your money is life's second-greatest tragedy. Don't ask what the greatest one is."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "What is life's greatest tragedy then?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Seymour",
                    "T": "I am aware of this one. It is \"to rest in your coffin without a single Mora to your name.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "I'm not sure I agree with those values. Aren't there many things more important than that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "Well, that's why I said \"don't ask.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Seymour",
                    "T": "I apologize."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "Anyway, based on the above reasons, I don't think the answer is a fancy timepiece, nor is it Mora."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What could it be, then?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Seymour",
                    "T": "The answer is simple — I can retrieve similar riddles with a 70% match rate."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Seymour",
                    "T": "This is from a centuries-old classic novel. It reads, \"I was born in the fleeting moment when eyes meet. I run with my back turned to the one I pursue.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Seymour",
                    "T": "\"Even after all flesh, bone, and entrails have been sliced away, I still lie nestled with you in the marrow that remains.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Seymour",
                    "T": "The answer is \"love.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "I get it now. This pocket watch is just like the one I have, then — It must be filled with memories of love."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Now, if only it would open."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "It will, one day."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "Why, well done, you silly dog! Who's the cutest mechanical dog?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Seymour",
                    "T": "It was my pleasure. \"Cute,\" however, is a subjective description. I would prefer to be addressed as \"the reliable, useful Prototype 4ACV07.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "And that's exactly what makes you so cute."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "Are you reenacting an old conversation? I feel like I've seen this scene before."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "In any case, someone's already solved this riddle. Let's get moving."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
